<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ติดต่อ Admin</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kanit:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
          body {
            font-family: 'Kanit', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            background-image: url('https://example.com/path/to/your/background-image.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: rgba(59, 89, 152, 0.9) !important;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
        }
        .navbar-brand, .nav-link {
            color: #ffffff !important;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .navbar-brand:hover, .nav-link:hover {
            color: #ffd700 !important;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .card {
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #3b5998;
            border: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(59, 89, 152, 0.2);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #2d4373;
            transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(45, 67, 115, 0.3);
        }
        .form-control {
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(59, 89, 152, 0.25);
            border-color: #3b5998;
        }
        .btn-link {
            color: #3b5998;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-link:hover {
            color: #2d4373;
            text-decoration: none;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('nav', { user: user, currentPage: currentPage }) %>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h1>ติดต่อ Admin</h1>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>หากคุณมีปัญหาหรือข้อสงสัยเพิ่มเติม สามารถติดต่อ Admin ได้ทาง Facebook:</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Facebook:</strong> 
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100014788909372" class="fb-link" target="_blank">ฐานิต แสงจินดา</a>
            </p>
            <p>เรายินดีให้ความช่วยเหลือและตอบคำถามของคุณโดยเร็วที่สุด</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>